data.title: GMJ Air Shuttle
data.meta_description: GMJ Air Shuttle | 713 followers on LinkedIn. Air Shuttle manages and operates an exclusive corporate aviation shuttle service and enterprise solution for a West Coast based Fortune 100 company. Operating a modern fleet of Embraer EMB-145XR aircraft. Air Shuttle provides up to 24 daily scheduled flights between four west coast cities, providing employees the ability to collaborate in real time and remain connected throughout the course of their travel day.
